Pre-requisite for the Feature Discovery Agent build system
=============================================

RHEL8 package Requirements
==========================
- Following RHEL 8 repositories should be setup and available (/etc/yum.repos.d) to download and resolve Feature Discovery Agent package dependencies
	BaseOS
	AppStream
	CodeReady
- dnf install git
- Ensure that the system date is properly setup (to PDT time)

How to Build
=============
- To build Feature Discovery Agent, 
#./fdagent_build.sh
- This script will generate a tarball(fd_agent.tar) and checksum file(fd_agent.sha2)
- Copy fd_agent.tar, fd_agent.sha2 and agent_untar.sh to a directory on the deployment machine

Repo Contents
=============
fdagent_build.sh 		Master build script which builds FD Agent and its SGX dependencies
build_prerequisites.sh 		Install RHEL 8 package dependecies required for Feature Discovery Agent build
download_dcap_driver.sh 	Download SGX dcap driver pre-built binary and adds to the tar file
install_sgxsdk.sh 		Downloads SGX SDK pre-built binary and installs it on build machine
download_sgx_psw_qgl.sh 	Downloads SGX PSW/QGL RPMS and adds it to tar file
download_mpa_uefi_rpm.sh 	Downloads Multipackage Agent UEFI RPM and adds it to tar file
build_pckretrieval_tool.sh 	Downloads DCAP PCKRetrieval tool and builds it adds to tar file
build_fd_agent.sh		Builds intel-secl-tee repo as a golang service and obtain fda bin
remove_pccs_connect.diff 	Patch file applied to PCKRetrieval tool to disable password check
